{"tid":1126914,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做人可以癲啲","createTime":"2019-04-26T16:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T18:27:18.000Z","uid":227650,"like":55,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c66df4f96f1ca3ce501784f621e9da9a2bf3f446","tid":1126914,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"我所指嘅「癲」唔係癲癲喪喪，而係指做人可以大膽啲、試多啲唔同嘅嘢、唔使太理其他人嘅睇法。<br />\n<br />\n做人下下循規蹈矩唔係話唔得，不過你嘅人生會少咗好多樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n攞我自己為例，我成日去旅行;亦都成日畀人話我嘥錢，但我唔理;我覺得人生係要見識多啲嘢。反正我錢夠洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你理得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699a7ed93fb70c005d9b33f72bbd74ba3acccf90","tid":1126914,"uid":196077,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"做過雞未"},{"pid":"5fca6f19213fad8ea4c17fa5120725d04e3576f2","tid":1126914,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"咁你見識到啲咩？<br />\n可唔可以分享下"},{"pid":"498f8359f96f2a8e8030ed7089ca13900cc535b5","tid":1126914,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fca6f19213fad8ea4c17fa5120725d04e3576f2","tid":1126914,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"咁你見識到啲咩？<br />\n可唔可以分享下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"成日去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6326482d6c3814f1358d69d68345d285d82a1b01","tid":1126914,"uid":227650,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5fca6f19213fad8ea4c17fa5120725d04e3576f2","tid":1126914,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"咁你見識到啲咩？<br />\n可唔可以分享下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:41:50.000Z","msg":"了解當地文化、知道佢哋一部份人鍾意啲咩同唔鍾意啲咩、嗰個國家嘅語言亦都有進步。<br />\n<br />\nBtw,呢個唔係重點。"},{"pid":"120be0f49729b7d2a371b7407f08605441a51765","tid":1126914,"uid":193476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,